::Rex/Firearm::

Rex transforms into his beast mode, the huge dinosaur looking around. He 
looks down at Arcangel, shaking his head.

"No good," he says, "We can still be detected, just a bit harder. There arn't 
enough of us to make a succesfull attack anyways."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Firearm stands still, not transforming. He looks around at the other bots in 
beast modes.

"No beast mode," he explains.
